  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nFrom the screenshot below, we can see the context tag displays the entire text \"sent contact request\" in a new line. The correct output should correctly wrap around the words.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/193580174-f3cbf42a-a69c-43d6-941f-fa3175d8e944.png\" width=\"600\" />\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nThe correct output should correctly wrap around the words, allowing for more text to be displayed in a single line.\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\nYou'll probably need to fix the private function `quo2.components.notifications.activity-logs/activity-context`.\r\n",
